title: Gashina (가시나)
lyrics: neoye ssaneulhaejin geu nunbichi nareul jugineun geo ya keoji deon ni mame bulsshi jaeman nameun geo ya wae shiga ni yagingabwa eojjae galsurok na yakhaja na seulpeun apeumdo hamkke mudyeojineun geo ya joa ijen neoreul ijeul su itge kkotgati sallae nadapge Can’t nobody stop me now naye hyanggil weonae moduga babocheoreom wae neoman molla jeongmal michin geo anya neon nal dugo tteonagashina geuri shwipge tteonagashina gati gaja go yaksokhaenogo ga shina gashina
